{"tid":805666,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[加利亞雷拉入金球] 森多利亞教練：如果係C朗入 一定會被吹大十倍 說到歷史金球","createTime":"2018-09-04T04:26:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T13:22:52.000Z","uid":54373,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d0cd76a855c13f03b6779390f90110829fa01b7","tid":805666,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:26:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/7Xk7LIak0_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F7Xk7LIak0_8&d=0cSX4lvwS2oF0OhBj3LQO4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8ac4bd03\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/7Xk7LIak0_8</a><br />\n<br />\n周一(3日)凌晨意甲爆出大冷門，森多利亞主場以3:0大炒上季亞軍拿玻里，爆出80倍波膽。<br />\n<br />\n其中埋齋一球更加係世紀金球，35歲老將加利亞雷拉接應右路傳中，背對龍門，跳起用後腳凌空射入，比伊巴謙莫域2004年歐國盃「蝎子腳」射入意大利大門，更加精彩。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">森多利亞教練甘柏路趁機「抽水」踩祖記球星C朗，話如果呢球波係由C朗射入，肯定被捧到上天，明顯寸緊呢位葡萄牙球星踢咗3場意甲仲未開齋，同埋證明意甲大把土炮前鋒屬於世界一流。</span><br />\n<br />\n事實上，加利亞雷拉以往經常射入金球，佢比C朗大兩歲，但入球率仍然相當高，上季意甲上陣35次射入19球，但卻一直被忽視，難怪甘柏路為佢抱不平。"},{"pid":"1bb4d16b29a7cf0f7727be67859609666d27b90d","tid":805666,"uid":11081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"樓主迷朗主席"},{"pid":"50afd717ebe7ebb507ca91d62541c07a36436e18","tid":805666,"uid":5649,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:29:33.000Z","msg":"邊能個牙，吾識喎"},{"pid":"e0f85df89af68e9ab8da10aa9a678a61a77b3424","tid":805666,"uid":53484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T04:32:12.000Z","msg":"世界波王"},{"pid":"9f91c7eb5f6acb381298e1d6470f33a6cff7cb08","tid":805666,"uid":112702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T05:04:43.000Z","msg":"有名你叫 波王 唔係靚波唔入<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過d人只識伊巴謙莫域 C朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61dff58da303932190598d16c282ca7127a9dd9","tid":805666,"uid":5166,"like":1,"dislike"